## Template Manifests (lib/manifests/templates/)

Templates using `envsubst` for variable substitution.

### Hardware Profiles
- `hardwareprofile-gpu.yaml.tmpl` - Generic GPU profile
- `hardwareprofile-gpu-small.yaml.tmpl` - Small (4B-8B models)
- `hardwareprofile-gpu-medium.yaml.tmpl` - Medium (8B-30B models)
- `hardwareprofile-gpu-large.yaml.tmpl` - Large (70B+ models)

**Variables:**
- `${NAMESPACE}` - Target namespace
- `${PROFILE_NAME}` - Profile name
- `${DISPLAY_NAME}` - Display name
- `${DEFAULT_CPU}`, `${MAX_CPU}` - CPU limits
- `${DEFAULT_MEM}`, `${MAX_MEM}` - Memory limits
- `${DEFAULT_GPU}`, `${MAX_GPU}` - GPU limits

### Model Serving
- `inferenceservice.yaml.tmpl` - InferenceService template
- `llminferenceservice.yaml.tmpl` - LLMInferenceService template

